flowchart TB
    A[Load Data (insurance.csv)] --> B[EDA (shape, head, info, describe, plots)]
    B --> C[Data Cleaning (drop duplicates, check nulls)]
    C --> D[Preprocessing: map sex & smoker -> is_female/is_smoker]
    D --> E[Categorical Encoding: one-hot encode region & bmi_category]
    E --> F[Feature Engineering: create bmi_category bins]
    F --> G[Feature Scaling: StandardScaler -> age, bmi, children]
    G --> H[Feature Selection: pearsonr, chi-square tests]
    H --> I[Train/Test Split: train_test_split (80/20)]
    I --> J[Model Training: LinearRegression.fit]
    J --> K[Prediction: model.predict]
    K --> L[Evaluation: R2, Adjusted R2]
    L --> M[Interpretation & Next Steps: feature importance, tune/try other models, deploy]